  "description": "As part of Cisco's ongoing commitment to proactive security and product quality, the Cisco RoomOS engineering team has conducted a comprehensive internal security review. This review resulted in a software hardening release that addresses multiple internally discovered vulnerabilities.\r\n\r\nThe vulnerabilities tracked by CVE-2026-20150 are related to improper access control&nbsp;that are grouped under the Common Weakness Enumeration (CWE) Pillar CWE-284.",
